[ both screaming ]

267
00:10:23,623 --> 00:10:24,916
Can | help you?

268
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,001
BOTH:
LSP!

269
00:10:26,084 --> 00:10:27,335
[ both scream ]

270
00:10:27,419 --> 00:10:29,254
