Ow! Ow! Hey! Hey, no!

271
00:10:29,337 --> 00:10:32,007
Oh, no!
What are you doing?!

272
00:10:32,090 --> 00:10:33,049
It was you.

273
00:10:33,133 --> 00:10:35,593
- You did it!
- Help me!

274
00:10:35,677 --> 00:10:37,762
| was just delivering
the pizza she ordered,

275
00:10:37,846 --> 00:10:39,639
and now she won't
let me leave.

276
00:10:39,723 --> 00:10:41,933
