280
00:10:47,605 --> 00:10:48,648
my heart!

281
00:10:48,732 --> 00:10:51,067
[ sobbing ]

282
00:10:51,151 --> 00:10:51,985
Hurry up, dude!

283
00:10:52,068 --> 00:10:54,738
- Shh!
- Right.

284
00:10:54,821 --> 00:10:56,573
Hoo! Thanks!

285
00:10:56,656 --> 00:10:58,783
- Shh!
- Go! Go!

286
00:10:58,867 --> 00:11:00,785
No tip, huh?
That's great.

287
00:11:00,869 --> 00:11:03,204
That's how it is around here.
Fine.

288
00:11:03,288 --> 00:11:05,498
Huh? Huh?
Come on, pal.

289
00:11:05,582 --> 00:11:06,916
Turns out the only case here

290
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:09,836
is just another case of LSP
being nutty.

291
